item.title: too many entries...
item.description: i need to update my blog. But i have too many entries sitting in my queue. far far too many. like 3. haha. but i really need to finish them. they are killing me. i think i will do that today. and then laundry. and then clean my room. and then work. wheee.. ok. now groceries.
